01:07:46,817 --> 01:07:47,818
[screaming]

1039
01:07:54,825 --> 01:07:55,868
[groans]

1040
01:07:56,618 --> 01:07:57,953
[sinister laughter]

1041
01:07:59,746 --> 01:08:01,123
[Caty] Unico!

1042
01:08:05,127 --> 01:08:06,170
Caty.

1043
01:08:07,129 --> 01:08:08,714
Oh, Beezle.

1044
01:08:09,381 --> 01:08:10,716
West Wind.

1045
01:08:10,966 --> 01:08:12,009
[water splashing]

1046
01:08:19,641 --> 01:08:20,726
[humming]

1047
01:08:24,771 --> 01:08:27,149
I'm... bored.

1048
01:08:30,903 --> 01:08:31,904
Huh?

1049
01:08:32,529 --> 01:08:33,572
[fantasy music]

1050
01:08:35,866 --> 01:08:37,576
Hey, there you are!

1051
01:08:38,202 --> 01:08:40,037
You come on God here, right now!

1052
01:08:40,245 --> 01:08:43,123
You're the one who took Unico
away from me.

1053
01:08:45,542 --> 01:08:48,170
[Beezle] Do you hear me?
You've got to tell me

1054
01:08:48,212 --> 01:08:49,296
where Unico is?

1055
01:08:51,215 --> 01:08:54,801
-Where is he? Where is he, huh?
- Unico is in danger.

1056
01:08:55,135 --> 01:08:58,305
What do you mean he's in danger?
What do you mean?

1057
01:08:58,639 --> 01:09:02,351
He's in great danger.
I'm on my way to him even now.

1058
01:09:02,684 --> 01:09:03,685
And I must hurry.

1059
01:09:04,353 --> 01:09:07,773
Ah, well, then I'm going too.
Unico is the only friend

1060
01:09:07,814 --> 01:09:11,235
I ever had.
You got to take me with you!

1061
01:09:14,571 --> 01:09:16,532
[gasps] It can't be.

1062
01:09:20,244 --> 01:09:22,329
Darkness is falling.
At any moment,

1063
01:09:22,371 --> 01:09:23,872
the Night Wind will be upon us.

1064
01:09:24,706 --> 01:09:26,875
If we're going to save him,
we got to get moving.

1065
01:09:27,084 --> 01:09:28,126
So be it.

1066
01:09:28,669 --> 01:09:30,462
I must take you
with me, little one.

1067
01:09:30,671 --> 01:09:32,464
[laughs] Oh, hurray!

1068
01:09:33,048 --> 01:09:34,675
Come on, let's make tracks.

1069
01:09:42,850 --> 01:09:44,685
She's moving faster than we are.

1070
01:09:45,143 --> 01:09:46,520
There is no way we can escape.

1071
01:09:48,772 --> 01:09:49,773
[West Wind gasps]

1072
01:09:50,274 --> 01:09:51,859
[Night Wind laughing]

1073
01:09:57,614 --> 01:09:58,907
[thrilling music]

1074
01:10:06,206 --> 01:10:07,291
[Night Wind laughing]

1075
01:10:08,750 --> 01:10:11,128
Look! I can see daylight
up ahead.

1076
01:10:15,382 --> 01:10:17,217
Hurry up! We're almost there.

1077
01:10:27,269 --> 01:10:28,270
[groans]

1078
01:10:30,147 --> 01:10:32,524
They've passed the boundaries
of my domain.

1079
01:10:32,774 --> 01:10:35,027
I am powerless before the light
of day.

1080
01:10:42,826 --> 01:10:44,453
[Beezle] We're coming Unico.

1081
01:10:45,495 --> 01:10:48,123
When darkness come again,
the Night Wind will return.

1082
01:10:48,457 --> 01:10:51,084
I must carry Unico far away
from this place.

1083
01:10:51,335 --> 01:10:52,878
Look, down there.

1084
01:11:07,643 --> 01:11:08,644
[Beezle] Unico!

1085
01:11:09,436 --> 01:11:10,646
Unico!

1086
01:11:13,023 --> 01:11:14,483
[groaning softly]

1087
01:11:22,074 --> 01:11:23,116
[happy music]

1088
01:11:25,536 --> 01:11:27,913
Beezle, is that really you?

1089
01:11:28,413 --> 01:11:29,873
Of course it is,
you little runt.

1090
01:11:30,123 --> 01:11:31,750
Who do you think it was, huh?

1091
01:11:32,000 --> 01:11:33,085
[laughing]

1092
01:11:33,585 --> 01:11:36,505
Oh, where's Caty?
What happened to her?

1093
01:11:38,423 --> 01:11:41,260
Caty? Caty?

1094
01:11:42,427 --> 01:11:44,805
He must have taken her
back into the castle.

1095
01:11:45,722 --> 01:11:48,392
Huh! So, this is the greeting
I get?

1096
01:11:48,475 --> 01:11:50,352
And after I came all this way.

1097
01:11:50,602 --> 01:11:52,938
Beezle, how did you get
here anyway?

1098
01:11:54,106 --> 01:11:55,440
[laughs]

1099
01:11:58,235 --> 01:12:00,112
-She brought me.
- Who?

1100
01:12:06,118 --> 01:12:07,327
West Wind!

1101
01:12:07,369 --> 01:12:09,288
Unico, the Gods know
where you are now.

1102
01:12:09,329 --> 01:12:10,914
You must come away with me.

1103
01:12:11,498 --> 01:12:13,083
Huh? I can't.

1104
01:12:13,834 --> 01:12:15,127
Nothing has changed.

1105
01:12:15,919 --> 01:12:17,754
If they find you,
they will send you

1106
01:12:17,796 --> 01:12:19,131
to the hill of oblivion.

1107
01:12:19,756 --> 01:12:23,051
No, I can't go with you yet.
I can't leave this place

1108
01:12:23,093 --> 01:12:24,678
until I've saved Caty.

1109
01:12:25,387 --> 01:12:27,723
There's no time for that.
Come, hurry!

1110
01:12:28,056 --> 01:12:29,850
Wait here. I'll be back soon.

1111
01:12:31,226 --> 01:12:32,936
Oh, Unico!

1112
01:12:38,692 --> 01:12:39,943
Hey, wait for me.

1113
01:12:48,869 --> 01:12:49,870
Whoa!

1114
01:12:51,663 --> 01:12:52,664
[sniffs]

1115
01:12:53,081 --> 01:12:56,460
You know... this place...
is kind of creepy.

1116
01:12:58,462 --> 01:13:00,255
[Caty] Unico!

1117
01:13:00,631 --> 01:13:01,965
[energetic music]

1118
01:13:04,635 --> 01:13:08,347
-Unico!
- Oh no! Caty!

1119
01:13:11,850 --> 01:13:12,851
Huh?

1120
01:13:14,478 --> 01:13:15,646
[crack of thunder]

1121
01:13:17,022 --> 01:13:20,150
[gasps] There's something rotten
about that guy.

1122
01:13:22,444 --> 01:13:23,861
Let her go!

1123
01:13:23,862 --> 01:13:27,241
Where's he going?
Hey, you don't stand a chance.

1124
01:13:27,366 --> 01:13:28,951
Come back! Hey!

1125
01:13:29,743 --> 01:13:30,744
Yeah!

1126
01:13:32,079 --> 01:13:33,163
[shouting]

1127
01:13:33,664 --> 01:13:34,790
[screaming]

1128
01:13:40,963 --> 01:13:42,047
Oh!

1129
01:13:42,673 --> 01:13:43,924
[shouting]

1130
01:13:55,727 --> 01:13:57,229
[loud rumbling]

1131
01:13:59,356 --> 01:14:00,357
[whimpers]

1132
01:14:06,488 --> 01:14:07,531
[thunderstorm]

1133
01:14:09,533 --> 01:14:10,909
Oh well. Here goes nothing.

1134
01:14:13,245 --> 01:14:16,206
Unico, don't just stand there.
Get a move on. Come on!

1135
01:14:17,416 --> 01:14:19,458
[Beezle] Don't mind me lady.
I'm just a friend of his.

1136
01:14:19,459 --> 01:14:20,544
Come on!

1137
01:14:21,253 --> 01:14:22,462
[eerie music]

1138
01:14:31,096 --> 01:14:32,139
-Whoa!
- Panting.

1139
01:14:37,144 --> 01:14:38,187
Whoa!

1140
01:14:38,896 --> 01:14:40,105
[thunderstorm]

1141
01:14:42,691 --> 01:14:43,734
[loud rumbling]

1142
01:14:59,750 --> 01:15:00,792
[roaring]

1143
01:15:07,424 --> 01:15:10,928
Wow! That guy is even meaner
looking than my dad.

1144
01:15:17,851 --> 01:15:18,894
[all shouting]

1145
01:15:55,639 --> 01:15:56,723
[shouting continues]

1146
01:16:06,316 --> 01:16:07,317
Oh!

1147
01:16:39,933 --> 01:16:41,101
[loud explosion]

1148
01:16:54,323 --> 01:16:55,616
[all panting]

1149
01:17:00,787 --> 01:17:01,830
Quick, grab on!

1150
01:17:02,581 --> 01:17:03,832
[groaning]

1151
01:17:15,511 --> 01:17:16,720
[shouting]

1152
01:17:31,985 --> 01:17:34,821
[gasps] The old woman!
She's in danger.

1153
01:17:38,575 --> 01:17:42,454
[sighs] That young lady.
Where could she have gone?

1154
01:17:50,003 --> 01:17:52,673
All the animals of the forest
will be destroyed.

1155
01:17:53,006 --> 01:17:54,633
Beezle, look after Caty.

1156
01:17:55,175 --> 01:17:57,845
No, Unico!
Have you gone crazy?

1157
01:17:58,095 --> 01:17:59,429
Come back!

1158
01:18:01,890 --> 01:18:03,225
[exciting music]

1159
01:18:04,017 --> 01:18:05,435
[Unico groaning]

1160
01:18:08,313 --> 01:18:09,314
[shouting]

1161
01:18:26,707 --> 01:18:27,708
[grunting]

1162
01:18:35,465 --> 01:18:38,468
-[Unico wailing]
- Oh no, Unico!

1163
01:18:39,178 --> 01:18:42,306
Ah! Lightning, come to me!

1164
01:18:50,063 --> 01:18:51,398
[roaring]

1165
01:18:52,858 --> 01:18:53,859
Uh-oh!

1166
01:18:55,068 --> 01:18:56,278
[screaming]

1167
01:18:58,447 --> 01:18:59,448
[coughs]

1168
01:19:02,784 --> 01:19:03,785
[grunts]

1169
01:19:07,998 --> 01:19:09,625
[thrilling music]

1170
01:19:11,793 --> 01:19:13,045
[roaring]

1171
01:19:20,552 --> 01:19:21,637
[shouting]

1172
01:19:24,056 --> 01:19:25,390
[shouting continues]

1173
01:19:29,019 --> 01:19:30,646
Unico!

1174
01:19:31,146 --> 01:19:33,065
Unico!

1175
01:19:39,613 --> 01:19:40,614
[Caty] Unico?

1176
01:19:41,782 --> 01:19:42,783
[crying]

1177
01:19:43,534 --> 01:19:47,788
Oh, no Unico,
I won't let you die. [sobbing]

1178
01:19:48,789 --> 01:19:49,873
[somber music]

1179
01:19:50,582 --> 01:19:51,625
[crying]

1180
01:19:54,086 --> 01:19:56,505
I'll give up being a human girl.

1181
01:19:57,506 --> 01:19:59,258
Just open your eyes.

1182
01:20:01,385 --> 01:20:02,678
[sobbing]

1183
01:20:08,642 --> 01:20:10,769
And I don't need
this stupid horn.

1184
01:20:11,520 --> 01:20:13,397
Look, I'll give it back to you.

1185
01:20:13,814 --> 01:20:15,148
Please open your eye.

1186
01:20:17,192 --> 01:20:18,402
[magical music]

1187
01:20:23,115 --> 01:20:24,116
Oh!

1188
01:20:25,242 --> 01:20:26,285
[shouts]

1189
01:20:28,537 --> 01:20:29,830
[epic music]

1190
01:20:39,298 --> 01:20:41,175
Thank you, Caty and Beezle.

1191
01:20:41,383 --> 01:20:43,426
I'm only able to take
on this form

1192
01:20:43,427 --> 01:20:46,555
because you've proven
that you truly love me.

1193
01:20:47,389 --> 01:20:48,390
Ah!

1194
01:20:48,891 --> 01:20:52,769
Oh Unico, Unico,
you're absolutely beautiful!

1195
01:20:53,061 --> 01:20:54,771
[exhilarating music]

1196
01:21:17,711 --> 01:21:18,795
[roars]

1197
01:21:56,291 --> 01:21:57,459
[loud rumbling]

1198
01:22:23,986 --> 01:22:26,154
-I don't believe it.
- Look at that.

1199
01:22:45,716 --> 01:22:47,259
[calm music]

1200
01:23:05,527 --> 01:23:06,820
[birds screeching]

1201
01:23:13,452 --> 01:23:14,661
[Caty and Beezle laughing]

1202
01:23:18,540 --> 01:23:20,374
Oh, I forgot about
the old woman.

1203
01:23:20,375 --> 01:23:21,710
I hope she's alright.

1204
01:23:23,712 --> 01:23:26,757
Unico, come on!
Get a move on!

1205
01:23:32,429 --> 01:23:34,264
It's all over now, Unico.

1206
01:23:34,723 --> 01:23:36,517
The Night Wind
will be here soon.

1207
01:23:36,892 --> 01:23:37,935
We must hurry.

1208
01:23:38,977 --> 01:23:40,562
[West Wind] Come, come now.

1209
01:23:41,647 --> 01:23:43,482
Caty, Beezle.

1210
01:23:44,024 --> 01:23:45,025
Goodbye.

1211
01:23:45,567 --> 01:23:47,736
[panting] Hello!

1212
01:23:56,912 --> 01:23:57,996
[emotional music]

1213
01:24:15,764 --> 01:24:17,391
-[Caty] Oh! [crying]
- Oh!

1214
01:24:23,480 --> 01:24:24,690
There you are.

1215
01:24:26,441 --> 01:24:27,985
I'll never leave you again.

1216
01:24:28,402 --> 01:24:29,403
Never.

1217
01:24:29,528 --> 01:24:30,737
[sobbing]

1218
01:24:31,405 --> 01:24:32,739
That's kind of sweet.

1219
01:24:35,242 --> 01:24:37,077
What the devil happened
to Unico?

1220
01:24:38,287 --> 01:24:39,288
Hey!

1221
01:24:40,163 --> 01:24:42,583
Hey, Unico!

1222
01:24:44,251 --> 01:24:45,335
Unico!

1223
01:24:46,211 --> 01:24:48,088
Where are you?

1224
01:24:52,301 --> 01:24:54,303
He wouldn't have gone again,
would he?

1225
01:25:01,685 --> 01:25:03,478
Are you ready to go Unico?

1226
01:25:04,396 --> 01:25:07,065
Caty... I hope you'll be
happy here.

1227
01:25:11,695 --> 01:25:13,697
Come to think of it,
whatever became

1228
01:25:13,739 --> 01:25:16,241
of that black kitty,
and that strange animal

1229
01:25:16,283 --> 01:25:17,618
with a little horn.

1230
01:25:17,826 --> 01:25:20,704
Oh, he'll be coming back,
don't you worry.

1231
01:25:20,954 --> 01:25:22,456
He saved my life, you know.

1232
01:25:22,831 --> 01:25:25,626
He used magic to do it.
He turned into a great

1233
01:25:25,667 --> 01:25:28,378
white horse with white wings,
and he flew into the sky,

1234
01:25:28,420 --> 01:25:32,049
-and killed the monster.
- A white horse with wings?

1235
01:25:32,883 --> 01:25:34,176
[happy music]
Then he was...

1236
01:25:35,677 --> 01:25:39,723
he was... a unicorn
without a doubt.

1237
01:25:41,058 --> 01:25:43,977
[woman] I've heard tales
of such a little unicorn

1238
01:25:44,019 --> 01:25:46,730
who has the wonderful gift
of bringing happiness

1239
01:25:46,772 --> 01:25:48,482
to any life he touches.

1240
01:25:50,108 --> 01:25:54,695
But, they say the little unicorn
is forbidden to stay for long

1241
01:25:54,696 --> 01:25:56,532
with those he has made happy.

1242
01:25:57,115 --> 01:26:00,160
What? What're you saying?
I can't believe that.

1243
01:26:00,202 --> 01:26:02,079
I won't let him go. I won't!

1244
01:26:03,038 --> 01:26:05,374
-Unico!
- No. Don't call for him,

1245
01:26:05,415 --> 01:26:09,253
my child. It won't do any good.
Neither he nor you

1246
01:26:09,294 --> 01:26:11,672
has any choice.
He must go away.

1247
01:26:12,130 --> 01:26:15,509
But he will protect
and watch over you from afar.

1248
01:26:16,593 --> 01:26:17,594
[gasps]

1249
01:26:17,928 --> 01:26:20,305
[yells] Unico!

1250
01:26:21,723 --> 01:26:24,101
Unico!

1251
01:26:27,312 --> 01:26:28,772
Unico!

1252
01:26:28,856 --> 01:26:30,607
Unico!

1253
01:26:31,191 --> 01:26:33,443
Where did you go to?

1254
01:26:37,322 --> 01:26:41,577
Oh! Oh, no, no, not again!
You can't take him away again.

1255
01:26:45,247 --> 01:26:46,248
[horn tinkles]

1256
01:26:47,666 --> 01:26:48,667
Whoa!

1257
01:26:50,919 --> 01:26:54,590
Hey, I don't want a horn.
I just want to go with you.

1258
01:26:54,840 --> 01:26:56,675
Take me with you.

1259
01:26:59,803 --> 01:27:01,054
Unico!

1260
01:27:01,305 --> 01:27:05,434
You can't get away from me.
I'll follow wherever you go.

1261
01:27:05,726 --> 01:27:07,394
Goodbye, Beezle.

1262
01:27:09,104 --> 01:27:11,815
[Caty] Unico!

1263
01:27:13,734 --> 01:27:15,527
Goodbye, Caty.

1264
01:27:16,486 --> 01:27:17,696
[bittersweet music]

